    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are assessed and meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 3. The equivalency of input parameters factor was not assessed on the basis that the team judged it inapplicable to a CFD comparative hemolysis study; all remaining evidence supports the conclusion that the model is fit for the intended COU. The package is accepted for regulatory submission.",
